    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Delete JAVA_HOME from the system variables and add the gradle directory: 'C:\\{gradle directory}\\bin' to the PATH variable. Close cmd, and reopen it. Write gradle -version and this should work if you're able to do &quot;java -version&quot;.</p>\n<p>Or</p>\n<p>Change JAVA_HOME to JAVACMD. Close cmd, reopen it, and write gradle -version.<br />\nCheck the gradle file.</p>\n"
  } ],
